00:01:31.720 --> 00:01:34.440
<i>~ Episode 1 ~</i>

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:41.509
<i>Do you know how the five regions
became the current five regions?</i>

00:01:41.510 --> 00:01:44.999
<i>The current Megrez Nation was
appointed by Holy Land Firmament</i>

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:49.049
<i>to overlord three nations, which are
Too-Deep, Plough, and Heaven Fiend.</i>

00:01:49.050 --> 00:01:51.679
<i>The nation prospers, and
the people are at peace.</i>

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:55.849
<i>However, a hundred thousand years ago,
Di Feitian massacred the five regions.</i>

00:01:55.850 --> 00:01:58.159
<i>People were in great misery and suffering.</i>

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.959
<i>The elder of Firmament, Chang Qingzi,</i>

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:05.420
<i>used Mystical Spirit Leaf to
turn around the war situation.</i>

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:13.129
<i>However, Di Feitian didn't
just disappear just yet.</i>

00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:18.589
<i>A few drops of his leftover blood
condensed into a Five-Colored Stone.</i>

00:02:18.590 --> 00:02:22.609
<i>And now, Di Feitian is about to come out.</i>

00:02:22.610 --> 00:02:28.510
<i>The one who awakens him will be a
girl who owns the Five-Colored Stone.</i>

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:33.129
<i>You are the one predestined
by the Mystical Spirit Leaf.</i>

00:02:33.130 --> 00:02:36.589
<i>Only you can change the universe.</i>

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:39.319
<i>Find the girl with the Five-Colored Stone.</i>

00:02:39.320 --> 00:02:44.850
<i>Or else, the five regions will
once again be doomed eternally.</i>

00:03:50.570 --> 00:03:52.909
- Who comes here?
- Fuyao.

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:54.999
For the third level of Mystic
Soul Five-Way Technique,

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:57.469
the person who can obtain the emblem of
Mystic Soul can get through this level.

00:03:57.470 --> 00:04:00.470
Okay. Then let's give it a try.

00:06:21.190 --> 00:06:24.749
How dare you! Why don't you bow
when you see your senior sister!

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:29.240
Senior Sister Pei is really
merciless when she fights.

00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:32.449
As a lowly factotum of
Mystic Black Section,

00:06:32.450 --> 00:06:34.499
how would you be qualified to
call me your senior sister?

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:37.379
Don't think that just because First Senior
Brother secretly taught you some Kung Fu,

00:06:37.380 --> 00:06:39.489
you can have the same level
and same treatment as I.

00:06:39.490 --> 00:06:43.659
Someone of low status will
forever be of low status.

00:06:43.660 --> 00:06:45.669
Some level and same treatment?

00:06:45.670 --> 00:06:46.919
That's good,

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:51.119
but unfortunately, I almost
learned that Kung Fu.

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.859
You wish!

00:06:52.860 --> 00:06:56.709
You violated the rules of Mystic Soul and
privately entered Five-Way Sanctum to cultivate.

00:06:56.710 --> 00:07:00.469
Today, I will definitely bring
you to see Clique Leader.

00:07:00.470 --> 00:07:03.879
I'd like to see who would speak up for you.

00:07:03.880 --> 00:07:05.459
Just a minute, just a minute.

00:07:05.460 --> 00:07:08.579
Senior Sister, I did
violate the clique rules.

00:07:08.580 --> 00:07:10.709
You want to bring me to
Clique Leader for punishment.

00:07:10.710 --> 00:07:13.349
However, if you want to catch the
thief, you must also have the loot.

00:07:13.350 --> 00:07:15.079
You have to catch me first.

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:18.660
Your death is imminent and yet you
are still stubborn with your words.

00:07:23.470 --> 00:07:25.389
A'Lie, tie her up!

00:07:25.390 --> 00:07:26.840
Yes.

00:07:41.570 --> 00:07:43.259
You are indeed an idiot.

00:07:43.260 --> 00:07:45.199
Below lies the bottomless cliff.

00:07:45.200 --> 00:07:47.779
If you have the ability, then jump.

00:07:47.780 --> 00:07:50.039
I am so scared.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:52.879
But since my senior sister
has commanded me to do so,

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:55.410
I will have to follow.

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:06.039
Miss.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:07.970
Idiot!

00:08:09.740 --> 00:08:11.709
This lowly servant!

00:08:11.710 --> 00:08:13.660
You will pay for it!

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:47.649
First Senior Brother!

00:08:47.650 --> 00:08:49.099
Fuyao!

00:08:49.100 --> 00:08:50.489
I saw someone from really far away.

00:08:50.490 --> 00:08:52.380
I knew it was you.

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:55.229
Why did you sneak out and
come down the mountain again?

00:08:55.230 --> 00:08:57.869
I told you many times already, you
can't sneak down on your own!

00:08:57.870 --> 00:08:59.109
If you get found out, you will be...

00:08:59.110 --> 00:09:01.089
I know! I just miss you!

00:09:01.090 --> 00:09:03.310
Full of nonsense!

00:09:04.590 --> 00:09:05.999
First Senior Brother.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:07.279
Junior Sister.

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:11.239
Senior Brother, you can't cover for
this lowly servant today anymore.

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:12.329
She is extremely daring.

00:09:12.330 --> 00:09:14.779
She actually dare to secretly enter
the cultivation sanctum to cultivate.

00:09:14.780 --> 00:09:16.109
And she was escaping by
running down the mountain.

00:09:16.110 --> 00:09:18.329
Who knows how many clique
rules she has violated?

00:09:18.330 --> 00:09:20.419
About this, we must
report to Clique Leader!

00:09:20.420 --> 00:09:22.090
She must be severely punished!

00:09:22.790 --> 00:09:25.249
Did that really happen?

00:09:25.250 --> 00:09:26.710
Yes.

00:09:29.520 --> 00:09:33.050
You! You always act so recklessly!

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:38.279
Junior Sister Pei, Fuyao is still young.

00:09:38.280 --> 00:09:39.649
It's understandable for her
to have some unruly behavior.

00:09:39.650 --> 00:09:42.019
Why don't you forgive her this time?

00:09:42.020 --> 00:09:45.899
First Senior Brother! You always
cover up for her like this!

00:09:45.900 --> 00:09:48.849
This lowly servant of Mystic Black Section
will disregard the rules even more often!

00:09:48.850 --> 00:09:50.909
Will our Mt. Mystic Soul
still have rules then?

00:09:50.910 --> 00:09:54.449
Speaking of rules, Senior Sister
Pei Yuan isn't any better.

00:09:54.450 --> 00:09:56.479
You! How dare you!

00:09:56.480 --> 00:10:00.119
Did I say anything wrong? Today is
the day of the sacrificial ritual.

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:03.929
All of the students of Mystic Main Section
should be waiting on the mountain.

00:10:03.930 --> 00:10:07.099
Senior Sister Pei Yuan is the First Senior
Sister of Mystic Main Section after all.

00:10:07.100 --> 00:10:09.199
Why did you secretly go
down the mountain, too?

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:10.589
You!

00:10:10.590 --> 00:10:12.390
Junior Sister Pei,

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.289
you are right in scolding her.

00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:17.709
I will report to Clique Leader later.

00:10:17.710 --> 00:10:19.930
I will make sure that she gets punished.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:24.389
You! When you go back,

00:10:24.390 --> 00:10:26.999
just stay at Mystic Black Section, face
the wall and reflect on your fault.

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:29.759
Later in the day, I will for sure
bring you to receive your punishment,

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:33.599
and teach you a good lesson. Hurry and go!

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.090
Yes.

00:10:36.690 --> 00:10:39.999
First Senior Brother! Why did
you let her go just like that?

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.620
Junior Sister!

00:10:55.220 --> 00:10:57.079
It's almost time.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:59.659
Why don't you follow me to
join the sacrificial ritual?

00:10:59.660 --> 00:11:02.220
<i>Sacrificial ritual?</i>

00:11:21.610 --> 00:11:23.620
- Greeting, Father.
- Greeting, Teacher.

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:48.939
We're going to have the hunting
game soon in our Mystic Soul.

00:11:48.940 --> 00:11:51.699
Under the blessing, we
have peace and prosperity.

00:11:51.700 --> 00:11:55.749
To the ancestors and masters, Student
Yan Lie would like to ask you

00:11:55.750 --> 00:11:59.099
to help us at Mystic Soul to
peacefully control Too-Deep Nation

00:11:59.100 --> 00:12:01.670
and win over the five regions again.

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:08.699
Help us at Mystic Soul to
peacefully control Too-Deep Nation

00:12:08.700 --> 00:12:11.520
and win over the five regions again.

00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:18.219
<i>I’m telling you, even though
this Mystic Soul Clique</i>

00:12:18.220 --> 00:12:20.279
<i>is a big clique in martial arts society.</i>

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:24.999
But, the ones who are really
qualified to learn martial art

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:27.939
are those staying on the
mountain, Mystic Main Section.

00:12:27.940 --> 00:12:34.319
Only those noble-born
students are qualified. Okay?

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:38.169
Our place here is called
Mystic Black Section.

00:12:38.170 --> 00:12:40.859
What is Mystic Black Section for?

00:12:40.860 --> 00:12:44.119
We are responsible of serving people.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:48.379
- No. Clean everywhere here.
- Yes, Uncle Zhou.

00:12:48.380 --> 00:12:51.949
- Uncle Zhou, these are the clothes you asked for.
- Good. Good.

00:12:51.950 --> 00:12:53.480
Take it.

00:12:54.740 --> 00:12:56.869
I’m telling you this way.

00:12:56.870 --> 00:13:00.659
Whoever wears clothes in this color,

00:13:00.660 --> 00:13:03.689
they are at the lowest rank.

00:13:03.690 --> 00:13:07.039
If you see whoever wearing
clothes in other colors,

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:09.379
you must avoid them all.

00:13:09.380 --> 00:13:10.990
Come here. Come here.

00:13:12.790 --> 00:13:14.830
I’m telling you,

00:13:16.130 --> 00:13:20.669
we have food and shelter here with

00:13:20.670 --> 00:13:24.669
no wind or no rain.

00:13:24.670 --> 00:13:28.139
How blessed we are.

00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:33.079
You have to work hard here,
never think of useless things.

00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:37.609
Don’t be like the children leader, Fuyao.

00:13:37.610 --> 00:13:41.910
I’m telling you, this Older Sis Fuyao...

00:13:48.850 --> 00:13:53.989
Where is Fuyao? Where is Fuyao?

00:13:53.990 --> 00:13:56.009
Where did Fuyao go?

00:13:56.010 --> 00:13:59.549
<i>Help us at Mystic Soul to
peacefully control Too-Deep Nation</i>

00:13:59.550 --> 00:14:01.749
<i>and win over the five regions again.</i>

00:14:01.750 --> 00:14:05.499
<i>Help us at Mystic Soul to
peacefully control Too-Deep Nation</i>

00:14:05.500 --> 00:14:08.269
- <i>and win over the five regions again.
- You scared me, Older Sis Fuyao.</i>

00:14:08.270 --> 00:14:10.009
Why did you just get here?

00:14:10.010 --> 00:14:12.999
You look quite handsome in this.
Where is mine? Where is mine?

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:14.909
- Here. Here.
- Let me see.

00:14:14.910 --> 00:14:18.199
You tell me, it's bad enough we wear cyan garments
to pretend as someone in Mystic Main Section.

00:14:18.200 --> 00:14:21.089
What if someone finds out that we watch
Clique Leader's sacrificial ritual secretly,

00:14:21.090 --> 00:14:22.329
I can’t imagine how we will die.

00:14:22.330 --> 00:14:24.499
There're so many people
in Mystic Main Section.

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:27.419
Who will notice whom?

00:14:27.420 --> 00:14:30.159
If we’re being so secretive like you,

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:32.139
we will look more suspicious. Be like me.

00:14:32.140 --> 00:14:34.159
Right, no one will recognize me.

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:37.039
But, you 're a trouble maker.
How will no one know you?

00:14:37.040 --> 00:14:39.679
This hunting game is only
held once per eight years.

00:14:39.680 --> 00:14:41.879
Of course we have to watch
the sacrificial ritual.

00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:43.739
We can learn something.

00:14:43.740 --> 00:14:45.059
If I've known, I won't take you here.

00:14:45.060 --> 00:14:47.770
Don’t be like this. I’m going. I’m going.

00:16:03.590 --> 00:16:09.669
Starting today, we are taking application
for the once-per-eight-year hunting game

00:16:09.670 --> 00:16:11.639
As long as you’re an adult
student under our clique,

00:16:11.640 --> 00:16:16.169
no matter you’re wearing white, cyan
or red garment, you can apply for it.

00:16:16.170 --> 00:16:18.939
No judging based on your
background but your skills.

00:16:18.940 --> 00:16:22.779
The hunting game was established by our
clique founder for him to form the clique.

00:16:22.780 --> 00:16:26.299
With many levels, it's established in
order to select the bravest student

00:16:26.300 --> 00:16:29.679
and help the citizens to get
rid of the mountain beasts.

00:16:29.680 --> 00:16:32.949
The winner will be the hero. What’s a hero?

00:16:32.950 --> 00:16:37.009
A person with the plant essence as his content
and the animal's power as his strength.

00:16:37.010 --> 00:16:39.649
Today’s winner will still be a hero.

00:16:39.650 --> 00:16:42.169
He will carry the honor
of Mystic Soul Clique

00:16:42.170 --> 00:16:44.699
and be the pillar of Too-Deep Nation.

00:16:44.700 --> 00:16:48.169
This is a game with both tests and honor.

00:16:48.170 --> 00:16:49.819
Whoever wants to participate

00:16:49.820 --> 00:16:54.139
has to put the application with your own
blood into this Celestial Fangding.

00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:57.559
Once you participate in it,
you life depends on the game.

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:59.139
Never regret.

00:16:59.140 --> 00:17:01.290
Not judging by our background.

00:17:01.820 --> 00:17:05.340
They’re still looking down on us from Mystic
Black Section, who’s wearing black garment.

00:17:06.940 --> 00:17:08.500
Am I wrong?

00:17:09.360 --> 00:17:10.909
Do you want to die?

00:17:10.910 --> 00:17:14.060
Quickly leave. Leave. Leave. Hurry. Hurry.

00:17:16.030 --> 00:17:19.079
Come down. Come down.

00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:21.959
Are you bullying me who don’t
know how to climb up the tree?

00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:27.889
I’m telling you, I’m going to beat
you to death if you come down.

00:17:27.890 --> 00:17:29.899
Is the sacrificial ritual
something you're allowed to go?

00:17:29.900 --> 00:17:33.879
It's not enough to cause the trouble
to yourself. You even dragged him in.

00:17:33.880 --> 00:17:36.399
Are you coming down or not?
Coming down or not?

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:39.919
I want to go down but I’m afraid
of height, I can’t go down.

00:17:39.920 --> 00:17:42.569
- This kid— - Uncle Zhou, don’t be angry.
Don't be angry.

00:17:42.570 --> 00:17:44.429
Older Sis Fuyao, quickly beg Uncle Zhou.

00:17:44.430 --> 00:17:47.019
If you’re helping her, don’t stop me then.
If not, I going to beat you too.

00:17:47.020 --> 00:17:50.029
- I'm going to beat you—
- Stop it. Stop it. Don’t beat him.

00:17:50.030 --> 00:17:52.449
- I forced him to go.
- No! It wasn't Older Sis Fuyao force me to go.

00:17:52.450 --> 00:17:54.749
- I went voluntarily. This really has— - I
don’t cared if you went voluntarily or not,

00:17:54.750 --> 00:17:56.179
go back and finish your dyeing jobs.

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:57.669
- Okay. Okay.
- Quickly leave.

00:17:57.670 --> 00:18:00.230
- Leave.
- Go. Hurry up.

00:18:03.180 --> 00:18:06.629
Come on. Uncle Zhou, you see, he left.

00:18:06.630 --> 00:18:08.659
Stop scolding me.

00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:10.839
And I went there just to watch.

00:18:10.840 --> 00:18:13.140
No one saw me.

00:18:14.390 --> 00:18:16.190
Come down.

00:18:16.990 --> 00:18:19.160
Come down and I won’t beat you.

00:18:22.730 --> 00:18:24.599
Come down and I will give
you a interesting job.

00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:26.429
I see.

00:18:26.430 --> 00:18:28.660
Today’s the 15th.

00:18:30.170 --> 00:18:32.719
Go down the mountain to get some wine.

00:18:32.720 --> 00:18:34.079
You’re letting me to go down the mountain?

00:18:34.080 --> 00:18:37.320
If you’re not going, I
will ask someone else.

00:18:38.290 --> 00:18:40.889
You. Finally you came down.

00:18:40.890 --> 00:18:44.219
Where did you go? You even
climbed the tree, didn't you?

00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:47.300
It’s painful.

00:18:48.650 --> 00:18:51.520
Stop hitting me. My butt hurts.

00:18:52.480 --> 00:18:54.880
Get up. Here.

00:18:57.420 --> 00:18:59.110
Let me see.

00:19:02.590 --> 00:19:04.569
Look at you, kid. I want to
beat you till you're clear.

00:19:04.570 --> 00:19:07.040
I really want to beat you a few more times.

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:15.860
Fuyao, be honest, why isn’t our
Mystic Black Section good?

00:19:16.550 --> 00:19:20.649
Right. Our rank is low. We’re poor.

00:19:20.650 --> 00:19:23.929
But, everyone treats you so well.

00:19:23.930 --> 00:19:27.229
Xiaoqi that group of children, follows you
around everyday. And what are you teaching them?

00:19:27.230 --> 00:19:29.299
Teaching to be like you and climb trees?

00:19:29.300 --> 00:19:31.289
You are always thinking of ways to
take off your black garment, right?

00:19:31.290 --> 00:19:33.119
What's wrong with me?

00:19:33.120 --> 00:19:35.219
I have a pretty good relationship with
everyone at Mystic Black Section.

00:19:35.220 --> 00:19:37.399
My relation with Xiaobai
is also quite good.

00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:40.789
- Then be a little more obedient.
- When was I disobedient?

00:19:40.790 --> 00:19:42.609
I just think it's unfair.

00:19:42.610 --> 00:19:44.529
Why do people have to be ranked
in different levels and status?

00:19:44.530 --> 00:19:46.719
Look at the people at Mystic Main Section.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:49.489
They can learn martial arts as soon as they
get in, and go wherever they want to go.

00:19:49.490 --> 00:19:52.149
And they even bully us! And
yet we have to serve them.

00:19:52.150 --> 00:19:55.399
Why is this? So our lives
are just worthless, right?

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:57.679
Stop talking anymore. This is all fate.

00:19:57.680 --> 00:20:01.209
It's fate so you will
just have to accept it.

00:20:01.210 --> 00:20:03.069
I am going!

